1
00:00:06,260 --> 00:00:10,420
[Under the Cover]

2
00:00:10,460 --> 00:00:13,380
[Episode 10]

3
00:00:13,380 --> 00:00:17,940
[People's Public Security]

4
00:00:17,940 --> 00:00:18,620
Hello.

5
00:00:18,620 --> 00:00:20,020
This is
the Jianghai Public Security Bureau,

6
00:00:20,020 --> 00:00:21,060
Anti-Fraud Unit.

7
00:00:21,080 --> 00:00:23,160
[Wang Jincheng]

8
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:28,420
[Billionaire Wang Jincheng.
Work with me. Target amount ?]

9
00:00:28,420 --> 00:00:30,500
Why would Han Chuan
target on Wang Jincheng?

10
00:00:31,380 --> 00:00:32,740
Target amount…

11
00:00:33,180 --> 00:00:34,620
How big is he aiming this time?

12
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:36,980
Mr. An.

13
00:00:37,380 --> 00:00:38,900
Wang Jincheng didn't pick up.

14
00:00:40,660 --> 00:00:42,380
He's the richest man in Jianghai,
with billions at his disposal.

15
00:00:42,500 --> 00:00:43,580
Do you think he'll take a random call?

16
00:00:43,860 --> 00:00:45,620
Mr. An, we've withdrawn the money.

17
00:00:49,340 --> 00:00:50,060
Return it

18
00:00:50,220 --> 00:00:51,300
to the folks who reported a case.

19
00:00:51,540 --> 00:00:52,220
And tell them,

20
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:53,260
next time when they get one of those

21
00:00:53,380 --> 00:00:54,940
9,999-yuan scam calls,

22
00:00:55,100 --> 00:00:55,860
having been scammed or not,

23
00:00:55,980 --> 00:00:57,020
contact us immediately.

24
00:00:57,300 --> 00:00:57,780
Got it.

25
00:01:01,080 --> 00:01:03,240
[Billionaire Wang Jincheng.
Work with me. Target amount ?]

26
00:01:03,860 --> 00:01:04,420
By the way, Yaqi.

27
00:01:05,660 --> 00:01:07,060
There will be more reports coming.

28
00:01:07,260 --> 00:01:08,580
The amount is unknown yet.

29
00:01:08,860 --> 00:01:09,740
Keep a close eye on it.

30
00:01:09,900 --> 00:01:10,780
See if anyone shows up.

31
00:01:11,460 --> 00:01:11,900
Okay.

32
00:01:22,020 --> 00:01:22,540
Mr. An.

33
00:01:24,460 --> 00:01:27,420
Do you have enough balance for it?

34
00:01:30,740 --> 00:01:32,860
Alas. It's for Han.
Until the last penny.

35
00:01:34,180 --> 00:01:34,780
Yang Yang.

36
00:01:35,340 --> 00:01:36,220
Come with me to Wang's place.

37
00:01:36,420 --> 00:01:36,900
Okay.

38
00:01:40,740 --> 00:01:41,340
Mr. An,

39
00:01:41,460 --> 00:01:42,100
we can handle

40
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:43,220
those 9,999 yuan calls.

41
00:01:43,380 --> 00:01:45,060
But if Mr. Han's asking for a million…

42
00:01:45,860 --> 00:01:47,060
are we going to sell our apartments?

43
00:01:47,740 --> 00:01:49,100
Han Chuan went through a lot

44
00:01:49,220 --> 00:01:50,900
to send us the hint
about scamming the richest guy.

45
00:01:51,100 --> 00:01:53,140
He must be in trouble over there.

46
00:01:53,980 --> 00:01:54,620
Let's go.

47
00:01:54,860 --> 00:01:55,300
Okay.

48
00:01:55,300 --> 00:01:57,140
[Anti-Telecom and Cyber Fraud Center]

49
00:01:57,140 --> 00:01:58,060
Officers,

50
00:01:58,180 --> 00:01:59,580
it's not that I won't let you in.

51
00:01:59,940 --> 00:02:01,140
We have rules here.

52
00:02:01,300 --> 00:02:02,100
Without the owner's consent,

53
00:02:02,260 --> 00:02:03,540
I can't let you enter.

54
00:02:04,380 --> 00:02:04,900
Look,

55
00:02:05,100 --> 00:02:06,380
this isn't some normal residential area.

56
00:02:07,620 --> 00:02:09,260
And Mr. Wang isn't back yet.

57
00:02:09,380 --> 00:02:10,500
When does he usually get back?

58
00:02:10,620 --> 00:02:11,580
I wish I knew.

59
00:02:11,780 --> 00:02:12,860
But how would I know that?

60
00:02:15,060 --> 00:02:16,100
That's Mr. Wang's car.

61
00:02:16,260 --> 00:02:17,300
Don't let him know I told you.

62
00:02:22,860 --> 00:02:24,180
Stop! Stop!

63
00:02:30,140 --> 00:02:30,980
Why is he running away?

64
00:02:31,420 --> 00:02:32,020
Wang Jincheng!

65
00:02:32,900 --> 00:02:33,460
Stop!

66
00:02:43,540 --> 00:02:44,180
Wang Jincheng!

67
00:03:03,740 --> 00:03:05,620
Why are you running, Wang Jincheng?

68
00:03:06,420 --> 00:03:07,020
You're…

69
00:03:08,660 --> 00:03:09,340
Yeah,

70
00:03:10,020 --> 00:03:10,940
why was I running?

71
00:03:11,740 --> 00:03:12,860
I didn't break the law.

72
00:03:13,220 --> 00:03:14,380
Why did you chase me?

73
00:03:14,540 --> 00:03:15,460
Because you ran.

74
00:03:15,660 --> 00:03:16,500
I ran because you were after me.

75
00:03:16,660 --> 00:03:17,340
Alright, alright.

76
00:03:18,620 --> 00:03:19,220
Wang Jincheng,

77
00:03:19,860 --> 00:03:20,300
we're here

78
00:03:20,460 --> 00:03:21,540
to ask for your cooperation.

79
00:03:22,020 --> 00:03:23,660
Co-cooperation?

80
00:03:26,020 --> 00:03:27,100
This guy, Wang Jincheng,

81
00:03:27,340 --> 00:03:28,300
refused to cooperate.

82
00:03:28,460 --> 00:03:29,980
I tried to convince him
as much as I can,

83
00:03:30,500 --> 00:03:31,580
telling him he'd only have to fake it,

84
00:03:31,660 --> 00:03:32,460
just playing along.

85
00:03:32,620 --> 00:03:33,860
But he kept saying no.

86
00:03:34,300 --> 00:03:35,420
I know this guy.

87
00:03:35,780 --> 00:03:36,900
We've dealt with him before.

88
00:03:37,180 --> 00:03:39,380
He's a total penny-pincher
and won't spend a cent.

89
00:03:39,580 --> 00:03:40,980
And he likes pocketing little things.

90
00:03:41,180 --> 00:03:42,860
He's so rich but steals from others?

91
00:03:43,820 --> 00:03:45,380
It's a mental problem, I think.

92
00:03:45,740 --> 00:03:46,900
If he doesn't take
something from others,

93
00:03:47,060 --> 00:03:48,140
he doesn't feel like himself.

94
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:51,060
The stuff he took wasn't pricey.

95
00:03:51,620 --> 00:03:53,140
We detained him a few times.

96
00:03:53,580 --> 00:03:54,580
He said he had changed.

97
00:03:55,100 --> 00:03:56,820
No wonder he bolted at the sight of us.

98
00:03:58,820 --> 00:04:00,540
But that habit lives in him.

99
00:04:01,460 --> 00:04:02,580
I've got an idea.

100
00:04:06,540 --> 00:04:07,260
Okay.

101
00:04:07,460 --> 00:04:08,700
Alright, babe.

102
00:04:10,020 --> 00:04:10,500
Buy it.

103
00:04:10,940 --> 00:04:11,940
We'll buy them all.

104
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:14,060
It's only several hundred thousand.

105
00:04:14,260 --> 00:04:14,900
I'll pay.

106
00:04:15,300 --> 00:04:16,380
I'll spend it on you.

107
00:04:16,820 --> 00:04:17,700
Don't be mad, okay?

108
00:04:18,660 --> 00:04:19,780
Hey, babe.

109
00:04:19,940 --> 00:04:21,340
I need to take this call.

110
00:04:21,940 --> 00:04:23,580
I'll buy them. I promise.

111
00:04:27,380 --> 00:04:27,940
Hello?

112
00:04:29,660 --> 00:04:30,180
Buddy,

113
00:04:30,900 --> 00:04:32,340
I know your voice by now.

114
00:04:32,980 --> 00:04:34,780
Stop calling me from new numbers.

115
00:04:35,540 --> 00:04:36,900
You're a scammer.

116
00:04:37,060 --> 00:04:38,860
You can't fool me.

117
00:04:39,140 --> 00:04:40,740
Even my dumbest move
is smarter than yours.

118
00:04:41,700 --> 00:04:43,020
Do yourself a favor, find another job.

119
00:04:44,020 --> 00:04:45,460
You're not cut out for this.

120
00:04:46,900 --> 00:04:47,340
Tsk!

121
00:05:08,580 --> 00:05:09,620
Got hung up again?

122
00:05:11,260 --> 00:05:13,540
I thought you were quite capable.

123
00:05:14,780 --> 00:05:15,900
I've been dying to find a chance

124
00:05:16,660 --> 00:05:18,140
to learn from you, respectfully.

125
00:05:21,820 --> 00:05:23,340
Less than six hours left.

126
00:05:24,340 --> 00:05:25,300
At this rate,

127
00:05:25,980 --> 00:05:27,940
it's bye-bye for you two.

128
00:05:30,260 --> 00:05:31,060
Have fun.

129
00:05:38,860 --> 00:05:39,900
What a jerk.

130
00:05:41,460 --> 00:05:41,900
Shisan.

131
00:05:42,740 --> 00:05:43,260
Shisan.

132
00:05:44,060 --> 00:05:45,300
I heard your sister had a high fever,

133
00:05:45,420 --> 00:05:46,300
and they wouldn't treat her.

134
00:06:14,340 --> 00:06:15,140
Any discount?

135
00:06:16,620 --> 00:06:18,100
Sorry, sir.

136
00:06:18,220 --> 00:06:19,820
This is the latest collection.

137
00:06:20,340 --> 00:06:20,940
No discounts.

138
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:24,260
A good knock-off will do.

139
00:06:26,140 --> 00:06:27,860
I'm really sorry, sir.

140
00:06:28,660 --> 00:06:29,500
Okay, okay, got it.

141
00:06:30,260 --> 00:06:30,900
I'll take it.

142
00:06:41,860 --> 00:06:43,180
Seriously,

143
00:06:43,700 --> 00:06:45,220
a rich guy with billions at hand

144
00:06:45,420 --> 00:06:46,580
swipes bottled water?

145
00:06:46,940 --> 00:06:48,860
Mr. An, is this really necessary?

146
00:06:50,340 --> 00:06:50,980
Wait a bit more.

147
00:07:05,020 --> 00:07:05,980
Sir, your bag.

148
00:07:06,540 --> 00:07:07,660
And your card, please.

149
00:07:08,300 --> 00:07:08,860
Bye.

150
00:07:09,460 --> 00:07:09,940
Sir,

151
00:07:10,300 --> 00:07:11,180
one moment, please.

152
00:07:11,340 --> 00:07:14,020
A belt that was placed here is missing.

153
00:07:14,180 --> 00:07:15,820
We may need to check your bag.

154
00:07:17,380 --> 00:07:18,860
Do you think I stole it

155
00:07:19,020 --> 00:07:19,660
from you?

156
00:07:19,980 --> 00:07:21,540
Forget your stupid belt.

157
00:07:21,700 --> 00:07:22,300
I could buy your store

158
00:07:22,420 --> 00:07:23,780
or even this whole building.

159
00:07:23,940 --> 00:07:24,940
Sir, sir.

160
00:07:25,060 --> 00:07:25,340
Sir.

161
00:07:25,460 --> 00:07:26,060
You… you can't leave!

162
00:07:26,260 --> 00:07:26,860
Hands off, you hear me?

163
00:07:26,940 --> 00:07:27,420
Hello.

164
00:07:28,420 --> 00:07:29,180
Police.

165
00:07:29,180 --> 00:07:29,940
Mr. An.

166
00:07:30,060 --> 00:07:30,820
Perfect timing.

167
00:07:31,500 --> 00:07:33,380
They're framing me for stealing a belt.

168
00:07:34,380 --> 00:07:36,780
Why do I bother? Stealing a belt?

169
00:07:36,940 --> 00:07:37,980
Isn't that ridiculous?

170
00:07:38,180 --> 00:07:39,900
We heard your talk just now.

171
00:07:40,180 --> 00:07:42,100
That belt wasn't stolen by him.

172
00:07:43,340 --> 00:07:44,180
He did it.

173
00:07:47,860 --> 00:07:50,100
Look, he's the one who stole it.

174
00:07:56,620 --> 00:07:57,700
If nothing went wrong,

175
00:07:58,340 --> 00:07:59,260
An Fei should have received

176
00:07:59,420 --> 00:08:00,660
the clues I sent back.

177
00:08:01,860 --> 00:08:03,620
Did he fail to crack it this time

178
00:08:04,460 --> 00:08:06,060
and fail to find Wang Jincheng?

179
00:08:07,900 --> 00:08:09,420
How's Xiaoxiao right now?

180
00:08:27,340 --> 00:08:28,140
Shisan,

181
00:08:29,260 --> 00:08:31,260
there is no time to zone out.

182
00:08:32,980 --> 00:08:35,180
We've got only five hours left.

183
00:08:38,260 --> 00:08:39,780
I handed you a whole list.

184
00:08:39,940 --> 00:08:41,740
If this one won't bite, try another.

185
00:08:42,180 --> 00:08:44,980
Why cling to this guy?

186
00:08:46,580 --> 00:08:47,060
You!

187
00:08:55,260 --> 00:08:55,820
No need.

188
00:08:57,540 --> 00:08:58,500
I'll try again.

189
00:08:59,100 --> 00:09:00,060
Gosh.

190
00:09:00,180 --> 00:09:01,300
Stubborn as a mule.

191
00:09:02,900 --> 00:09:03,700
Sihai,

192
00:09:06,980 --> 00:09:10,020
I'm bringing the boys here

193
00:09:10,140 --> 00:09:11,300
to learn from Shisan.

194
00:09:12,140 --> 00:09:12,980
Do you mind?

195
00:09:19,940 --> 00:09:21,020
I might miss the show

196
00:09:21,260 --> 00:09:22,460
if I come any time later.

197
00:09:22,620 --> 00:09:24,020
Why are you so mean?

198
00:09:24,140 --> 00:09:25,580
Can't you say something nice?

199
00:09:26,340 --> 00:09:26,940
Take notes.

200
00:09:27,860 --> 00:09:29,020
Watch and learn.

201
00:09:29,700 --> 00:09:30,260
Learn well.

202
00:09:32,660 --> 00:09:33,260
Mr. Wang,

203
00:09:34,020 --> 00:09:35,140
let's have a video chat.

204
00:09:35,580 --> 00:09:37,540
You'll know I'm not
a scammer when you see me.

205
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:48,140
Oh, it's real.

206
00:09:48,940 --> 00:09:49,700
I'm so sorry.

207
00:09:49,820 --> 00:09:50,500
My apologies.

208
00:09:50,700 --> 00:09:52,380
I swear I didn't mean it.

209
00:09:52,740 --> 00:09:54,820
I've got too many scam calls lately.

210
00:09:55,060 --> 00:09:56,300
My apologies.

211
00:09:58,820 --> 00:10:00,260
Let me confirm your info again.

212
00:10:01,020 --> 00:10:01,860
Wang Jincheng,

213
00:10:02,700 --> 00:10:04,660
legal rep and chairman

214
00:10:04,820 --> 00:10:05,820
of Jianghai Jincheng New Energy Group,
right?

215
00:10:06,180 --> 00:10:06,700
Yes.

216
00:10:07,180 --> 00:10:09,220
According to the tax system,

217
00:10:09,460 --> 00:10:11,820
your company's involved
in tax evasion or avoidance.

218
00:10:12,140 --> 00:10:13,940
You need to pledge assets

219
00:10:14,540 --> 00:10:16,340
and let the Tax Bureau
audit your bank flows.

220
00:10:17,020 --> 00:10:17,740
Alright.

221
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:23,020
[Hesitate]

222
00:10:23,020 --> 00:10:24,220
It feels like…

223
00:10:24,620 --> 00:10:25,180
No.

224
00:10:26,260 --> 00:10:27,300
That can't be right.

225
00:10:27,980 --> 00:10:30,180
I always pay tax strictly by the book.

226
00:10:30,380 --> 00:10:31,180
Every time.

227
00:10:33,060 --> 00:10:34,740
Have you ever tried to reduce tax?

228
00:10:34,740 --> 00:10:35,860
[Yes.]

229
00:10:35,860 --> 00:10:37,060
Well...

230
00:10:38,220 --> 00:10:39,820
That was legal at the time.

231
00:10:39,980 --> 00:10:42,100
What used to be legal
isn't necessarily legal now.

232
00:10:42,900 --> 00:10:43,700
Wang Jincheng,

233
00:10:45,220 --> 00:10:46,420
you've got a sister, right?

234
00:10:47,500 --> 00:10:48,740
S-sister?

235
00:10:54,780 --> 00:10:56,420
It doesn't say anything
about a sister here.

236
00:10:58,940 --> 00:11:00,460
Which sister are you talking about?

237
00:11:00,580 --> 00:11:03,220
You know exactly which one.

238
00:11:04,380 --> 00:11:06,060
You used her company as cover

239
00:11:06,340 --> 00:11:07,420
[Xiaoxiao]
to evade taxes.

240
00:11:07,940 --> 00:11:09,220
Do you think we can't trace it?

241
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,440
[Admits it.]

242
00:11:12,660 --> 00:11:14,740
Officer, I was wrong.

243
00:11:15,580 --> 00:11:16,580
I got greedy.

244
00:11:16,780 --> 00:11:17,580
Wang Jincheng,

245
00:11:17,820 --> 00:11:18,660
listen up.

246
00:11:19,780 --> 00:11:21,820
What I say next is critical.

247
00:11:22,940 --> 00:11:25,300
The state is cracking
down hard on tax evasion.

248
00:11:25,940 --> 00:11:27,500
Penalties are severe.

249
00:11:28,980 --> 00:11:30,700
Han Chuan's in danger in that place.

250
00:11:31,340 --> 00:11:34,060
[He's at risk.]
You must pay all dues by 6 p.m.

251
00:11:34,780 --> 00:11:35,540
Otherwise,

252
00:11:36,020 --> 00:11:36,860
not just you,

253
00:11:37,180 --> 00:11:39,020
we'll go after your sister, too.

254
00:11:39,540 --> 00:11:41,060
If the money isn't in by six,

255
00:11:41,420 --> 00:11:43,260
both he and Xiaoxiao are in danger.

256
00:11:43,260 --> 00:11:44,420
[Six o'clock. Xiaoxiao.]

257
00:11:44,420 --> 00:11:45,140
But

258
00:11:45,860 --> 00:11:48,260
as long as you stop doing it again,

259
00:11:48,940 --> 00:11:50,260
the government
won't make it hard for you.

260
00:11:50,740 --> 00:11:51,780
[After this challenge...]
Getting past this,

261
00:11:52,180 --> 00:11:54,340
Han Chuan and Xiaoxiao
will be safe for now.

262
00:11:55,620 --> 00:11:57,260
My superiors have made it clear

263
00:11:57,980 --> 00:11:59,340
that once the penalties are received,

264
00:11:59,900 --> 00:12:01,500
you don't need to worry
about anything else.

265
00:12:02,420 --> 00:12:03,540
We'll take care

266
00:12:03,700 --> 00:12:05,140
of the rest of the procedure for you.

267
00:12:05,780 --> 00:12:06,740
You'll be fine.

268
00:12:08,780 --> 00:12:10,260
[Intercept laundering]
Han needs the funds in,

269
00:12:10,620 --> 00:12:12,940
so we can intercept
during money laundering.

270
00:12:13,420 --> 00:12:14,260
Got it?

271
00:12:20,500 --> 00:12:22,180
Got it. I got it.

272
00:12:24,180 --> 00:12:24,860
Officer,

273
00:12:25,260 --> 00:12:28,260
how much do I need to pay?

274
00:12:29,420 --> 00:12:30,060
Twenty million.

275
00:12:33,980 --> 00:12:35,700
[Billionaire Wang Jincheng.
Work with me. Target amount ?]

276
00:12:35,700 --> 00:12:37,060
Twenty million!

277
00:12:42,940 --> 00:12:43,980
[Agreed]

278
00:12:46,780 --> 00:12:47,860
Twenty million.

279
00:12:58,400 --> 00:12:59,640
[Calling…]

280
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:00,160
[Call declined]

281
00:13:05,860 --> 00:13:06,460
That's it?

282
00:13:07,060 --> 00:13:08,020
You scared him off.

283
00:13:11,420 --> 00:13:14,180
Trying to get twenty million
out of one guy.

284
00:13:15,420 --> 00:13:16,660
How dare you!

285
00:13:18,220 --> 00:13:19,900
No one here could pull this off

286
00:13:20,580 --> 00:13:21,460
but you, huh?

287
00:13:21,660 --> 00:13:22,580
Now look at you.

288
00:13:22,820 --> 00:13:23,460
Look at you!

289
00:13:23,780 --> 00:13:24,980
Keep your mouth shut, will you?

290
00:13:25,380 --> 00:13:27,500
Your failure isn't his.

291
00:13:27,940 --> 00:13:28,700
My failure?

292
00:13:29,020 --> 00:13:29,700
That's fine.

293
00:13:33,060 --> 00:13:33,860
Shisan,

294
00:13:35,140 --> 00:13:36,420
if you can't do it,

295
00:13:37,180 --> 00:13:38,380
people will die.

296
00:13:39,300 --> 00:13:39,860
Two people.

