00:13:42,700 --> 00:13:43,500
Two.

298
00:13:46,940 --> 00:13:47,460
Let's go.

299
00:13:48,500 --> 00:13:49,420
You lot.

300
00:13:53,140 --> 00:13:54,740
Nothing good ever comes
out of his mouth.

301
00:13:57,060 --> 00:13:57,620
Shisan,

302
00:13:58,660 --> 00:13:59,780
