303
00:14:01,860 --> 00:14:02,620
We've got time.

304
00:14:03,860 --> 00:14:04,540
Wait it out.

305
00:14:19,580 --> 00:14:20,020
Mr. Wang, listen.

306
00:14:20,140 --> 00:14:21,220
I really can't do this.

307
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:23,020
Pack up. Please leave now.

308
00:14:23,820 --> 00:14:24,580
I'm telling you,

309
00:14:25,020 --> 00:14:25,820
Officer,

310
00:14:25,980 --> 00:14:27,380
sorry, I can't help you.

311
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:28,540
Find someone else.

312
00:14:28,700 --> 00:14:29,780
Mr. Wang, please.

313
00:14:29,940 --> 00:14:30,700
