not without hesitation though.

322
00:14:45,420 --> 00:14:46,420
It's a rescue, right?

323
00:14:46,820 --> 00:14:49,180
But he said twenty million!

324
00:14:49,380 --> 00:14:50,140
I'm rich,

325
00:14:50,620 --> 00:14:52,100
