326
00:14:52,260 --> 00:14:53,780
Do you know my annual profit?

327
00:14:54,060 --> 00:14:54,740
Mr. Wang.

328
00:14:54,940 --> 00:14:55,660
Mr. An,

329
00:14:55,780 --> 00:14:57,460
