330
00:14:57,780 --> 00:14:59,300
Mr. Han is your buddy.

331
00:14:59,460 --> 00:14:59,900
But

332
00:15:01,420 --> 00:15:02,820
I don't know him.

333
00:15:02,940 --> 00:15:04,260
We're not relatives or friends.

334
00:15:04,420 --> 00:15:05,180
Why should I risk it?

335
00:15:05,340 --> 00:15:06,340
Honestly, why should I?

336
00:15:06,540 --> 00:15:07,100
You guys,

337
00:15:07,940 --> 00:15:08,980
find someone else.

338
00:15:09,300 --> 00:15:10,340
Please leave now.

339
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:11,540
Sorry, Officers.

340
00:15:11,740 --> 00:15:12,660
Pack your things.

341
00:15:12,660 --> 00:15:13,700
Go, go, go.

342
00:15:13,900 --> 00:15:14,500
Please leave.

343
00:15:14,660 --> 00:15:15,500
Sorry about that.

344
00:15:15,500 --> 00:15:16,100
Please leave.

